title: Antony and the Johnsons - Live at Dalhalla 2007 good quality
description:
When Antony and the Johnsons performed at the
outdoors theater Dalhalla in june 2007, the 
Swedish national radio recorded the event. It 
was broadcasted in "P3 Live" 30 january 2008.

01 Mysteries of Love
02 For Today I am a Boy
03 Cripple and the Starfish
04 "I've been thinking a lot about rocks"
05 Deeper than Love
06 "Thank you"
07 I Fell in Love With a Dead Boy
08 Crazy in Love
09 Fistful of Love
10 You Are My Sister
11 Twilight
12 Hope There's Someone
13 Bird Gehrl
14 "I don't have anymore songs"

It's all in good quality.
